# quiz.py

## Questions ##
Q: How many siblings does Ronald Weasley have? A: 6
Q: How many wizarding children fit the description of the prophecy? A: 2
Q: Who was the other child who fit the prophecy besides Harry? A: Neville Longbottom
Q: How many horcruxes did Voldemort create? A: 7
Q: What is the seventh horcrux? A: Harry Potter
Q: What is Voldemorts Birth Name? A: Tom Marvolo Riddle
Q: Who taught Tom Riddle about Horcruxes? A: Horace Slughorn
Q: What is Harry Potters Grandmothers Maiden Name? A: Dorea Black 
Q: What witch did Severus Snape grow up near? A: Lily Evans


answer = input("When was the first known use of the word 'quiz'? ")
if answer == "1781":
    print("Correct!")
else:
    print(f"The answer is '1781', not {answer!r}")
